39:44.529 --> 39:46.326
more penetration
than all the static shots.

39:46.397 --> 39:48.262
So we are getting
more penetration,

39:48.332 --> 39:52.792
but it's not the double
that the myth actually claims.

39:52.870 --> 39:54.064
Fire.

39:55.440 --> 39:56.771
NARRATOR:
If it was double,

39:56.841 --> 39:58.809
these arrows
would have buried themselves

39:58.876 --> 40:00.969
all the way
up to their feathers.

40:01.045 --> 40:02.672
Okay, Kari.
So, what do you got?

40:02.747 --> 40:05.682
Well, for the static shots,
I got an average of 8.77.

40:05.750 --> 40:07.081
Now, for the moving shots,

40:07.151 --> 40:09.415
I got an average
of 11.04 inches.

40:09.487 --> 40:11.387
All right, well,
before we call this one busted,

40:11.456 --> 40:13.083
I think we need to go back
to the shop,

40:13.157 --> 40:14.681
double-check the high speed

40:14.759 --> 40:16.249
and see what the speeds
of the arrows were.

40:16.327 --> 40:19.353
[All cheering]

40:19.430 --> 40:21.455
The key to this myth
is penetration.

40:21.532 --> 40:24.126
But after measuring our arrows,
this one's busted.

40:24.202 --> 40:25.464
Yeah, and we used bead foam,

40:25.536 --> 40:27.936
which has a similar density
to both our ballistic material

40:28.005 --> 40:31.338
and the human body, and we
only got 25% more penetration,

40:31.409 --> 40:33.809
which is far from
what their stories told.

40:33.878 --> 40:36.005
And that was backed up
by our high-speed footage,

40:36.080 --> 40:37.843
which showed that our iron horse

40:37.915 --> 40:40.748
increased the speed
of our arrows by 31%,

40:40.818 --> 40:44.549
resulting in only a 72% increase
in kinetic energy.

40:44.622 --> 40:45.611
Not quite double.

40:45.690 --> 40:46.782
Yeah, but you got to give it
to them...

40:46.858 --> 40:49.019
Riding horseback did give them
some advantage.

40:49.093 --> 40:51.857
It just wasn't exactly as much
as they bragged about.

40:51.929 --> 40:53.794
Yeah, but that being said,
the arrows still didn't go

40:53.865 --> 40:55.730
twice as deep,
so this one's busted.

